snippet.title: Top 10 Reasons Amber Heard Was Cancelled
snippet.description:
Top 10 Reasons Amber Heard Was Cancelled

Amber Heard and Johnny Depp's names have been all over the media these past few years, with tales of their toxic relationship and harrowing divorce being the centre of the internets attention. For a while Amber had people believing her as the victim of the situation, but as more and more evidence came out it was clear to see that it was in fact Johnny who had been suffering at her hand. With the sheer amount of awful things that she's done, we have a list of all the reasons she's been cancelled. These are the Top 10 Reasons Amber Heard Was Cancelled here on Top 10 Beyond the Screen!
